@startuml http_jsonrpc_server_sequence
!theme plain
autonumber

title HttpJsonRpcServer JSON-RPC 请求处理时序图

actor "HTTP Client" as Client
participant "HttpJsonRpcServer" as HTTP
participant "cpp-httplib\n(Server)" as Server
participant "JsonRpc\n(Protocol)" as RPC
participant "MethodHandler\n(User Code)" as Handler
participant "SSE Endpoint\n(Optional)" as SSE

== JSON-RPC 请求处理 ==

Client -> HTTP: POST /\n{jsonrpc:"2.0",method:"add",params:[1,2],id:1}
activate HTTP

HTTP -> Server: 接收 HTTP 请求
activate Server
Server -> HTTP: 回调请求处理器
deactivate Server

HTTP -> RPC: handleRequest(jsonBody)
activate RPC

RPC -> RPC: 解析 JSON 请求
RPC -> RPC: 验证请求格式

RPC -> Handler: 调用已注册的方法\nmethod="add", params=[1,2]
activate Handler
Handler --> RPC: 返回结果\nresult=3
deactivate Handler

RPC --> HTTP: 返回响应\n{jsonrpc:"2.0",result:3,id:1}
deactivate RPC

HTTP -> Server: 设置响应头\nContent-Type: application/json
activate Server
Server --> HTTP: 响应准备完成
deactivate Server

HTTP --> Client: HTTP 200 OK\n{jsonrpc:"2.0",result:3,id:1}
deactivate HTTP

== SSE 实时推送 (可选) ==

Client -> HTTP: GET /events\n(建立 SSE 连接)
activate HTTP

HTTP -> Server: 设置 SSE 响应头\nContent-Type: text/event-stream
activate Server
Server --> HTTP: 建立持久连接
deactivate Server

HTTP -> SSE: 生成客户端ID\n连接回调
activate SSE
SSE --> HTTP: 连接确认\n{clientId:"abc123"}
deactivate SSE

HTTP --> Client: event: connected\ndata: {"clientId":"abc123"}\n\n

note over Client,SSE
    连接保持打开状态
    服务器可以随时推送事件
end note

... 随时间推移 ...

Handler -> HTTP: 业务逻辑产生事件\n需要推送
activate HTTP

HTTP -> SSE: broadcastSseEvent\nevent="update", data={...}
activate SSE
SSE --> HTTP: 格式化 SSE 事件
deactivate SSE

HTTP --> Client: event: update\ndata: {...}\n\n

== 连接关闭 ==

Client -> HTTP: 连接断开
HTTP -> SSE: 连接断开回调\nconnected=false
activate SSE
SSE --> HTTP: 清理客户端资源
deactivate SSE
HTTP --> Client: 连接关闭
deactivate HTTP

@enduml
